Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Never ignore the power of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Its limits rely on the wielder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today we visit the game center.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We'll be playing a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.14,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:47.02,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,The Battle Game Trap\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Battle Game Trap, Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew a place Sonoko likes wouldn't be too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is far from school, not many know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can take a wedding photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, that wasn't there yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can take pictures seperately as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with different looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to give a photo to Kyougoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like when Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} got a\Nfan letter from a girl and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Is it alright to send photos of your face to others?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's sad, Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} has been so busy since he quit\Nas the basketball coach and joined the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} isn't around, Sensei\Nis the most popular person at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh Sonoko, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The new English teacher Jodie is popular, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one with the revealing clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the guys like having a teacher that wears such clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't you wear them as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she still teaches well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's too serious all the time and doesn't make it fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's always so reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wears such revealing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally got an American at our school\Nand she doesn't even tell jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here, at an arcade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't those Teitan uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a high-school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No no no no, you've got the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You always come to this arcade after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Japanese games are beautiful and exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:09.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In America, everyone loves Japanese games!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.99,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Jodie Saintemillion (28)\NTeitan High School Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are always long lines to play in arcades there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you don't even get to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always loved playing these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's a gamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the school doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if they find out it'll be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so hard for an American to find a job in Japan, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's keep this our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one has to know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're like Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Do you all want to play something more exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the number one fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great Fighter Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put on your headgear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A coin for stand by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we pick the player character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.17,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Punch with the right lever to start, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That stings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, a player actually feels the hits\Nin this virtual fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's too much for girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, Ran! There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great! Ran is a well known karate champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Champ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Someone's joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That player over there has challenged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's very skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:56.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you've lost, it's time to move, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:34.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That seat is reserved for skilled players like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.66,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Bitou Kengo (21)\NUnemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you must take revenge, revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because he doesn't just use his hands and feet, he also uses the punchkey to apply full force in his attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:58.72,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Dejima Hotoshi (22)\NStore Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:58.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You won't beat him on your first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, hurry this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This seat was made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's with that guy's attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the local champion that uses the character Beika Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:24.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He's joined some gang recently and developed\Neven more of an attitude problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:24.58,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Emori Toshitsugu (41)\NTaxi Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way girl, your actions have too much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a game, so don't use so much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch how he only moves his body slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You watched our fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it on the big screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uusually there's only a scrolling image there,\Nbut when a match begins it shows it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:10:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone could beat him they'd become the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:08.55,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Shimizu Takayasu (30)\NGame Journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I fit the part, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've been waiting, partner. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm gonna smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go now, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right right, this isn't the only arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's play this racing game please, one more chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing! Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're gonna get the high-score!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I guess she's a big gamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two guys are fighting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget them and watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, something is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's winning? This game doesn't have a hit-point gauge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being hit in the face, it turns blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who beat me is winning right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, looks like that's the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido Lucas just didn't have it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opponent can't even get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll only take one more hit until he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He better hurry, time's running out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, that moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would have won with just one more hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}D-Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Someone died battling in a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all watching the fight as\Nit happened on this big screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right when he was about to win, he stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after checking the body, you all discovered he was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Bitou Kengo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 21 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has a reputation for bad behavior at this game center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so he has enemies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's my dad's old partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my high-school's English teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Jodie Saintemillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Juuzou Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Japanese "poriceman".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Porice?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not "poriceman," it's "policeman."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, "poriceman?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No no no no, policeman, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Poriceman?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the problem is how he died playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The witnesses said that no one entered the game\Ncenter or got near the victim during the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bitou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have ate anything during\Nthe game, so that rules out a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is he wearing this stuff to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a virtual reality game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When hit by the opponent, the player\Nfeels pain in the impacted area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The player feels pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when you're hit by the opponent, you'll feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This causes the players arms and legs to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making the fight seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it's pain, it's still only a mild vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how can that kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't strong enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am the one that was fighting with\Nhim in the game before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shouldn't make me a murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was the one who lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only got in a few good hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost even while chewing my special gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was losing the entire match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still don't know how he died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we couldn't find any apparent physical injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he looks like he died due to suffocation,\Nbut there are no marks on his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it isn't poison then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he died playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't eat while playing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he would have eaten something before,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body would have been weak and his\Nface would have changed color, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did any of you notice that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before this battle, the victim beat Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But couldn't it have been injected through a needle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he have been angry with whoever had done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone would have noticed him yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Inspector, aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a game center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quiet right now because the games are\Noff, but usually it's very loud in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not to mention, his hands and\Nfeet are bound to the game chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually it's very dark in here so the\Ngames will work correctly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, the victim wouldn't have been able\Nto yell for help even if he was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if everyone here was looking at the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Order an autopsy immediately and find the cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, find the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how are we going to find suspects\Nwith so many people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know everyone that was near the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because before he died, I was with the others\Nwatching Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} play a racing game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who are the people that got near him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That young store employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This tall man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with the four of us, that's six people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, but we weren't the only ones to see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That did as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that camera recording at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, can we take you six to watch the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone please follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It sounds like metal scratching something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And rubbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:21.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, here! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is about to sit down in the game chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just after he took the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is you, Dejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was collecting the coins from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Shimizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are you two talking about there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was preparing my battle strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What'd you pick up from the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dropped my lighter, so I was picking it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then the game started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Inspector! Look at Dejima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's holding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A video?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I record the exciting fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hit after hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and the others moved away from the racing game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we wanted to watch the exciting fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was alone and\Nnear the victim for a moment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! But I was focused on playing the racing\Ngame and didn't notice anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, you had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei really had to have been playing the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because just when everyone went to the\Nvictim's body, she got the high-score.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's likely innocent, because her\Ndriving got her the high-score.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to focus to do that on a racing game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey! Someone is behind the victim's chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the guy playing the mahjong game!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the guy that talked bad about the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Bring that man here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is the one that committed this murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:58.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something about that match,\NI know there's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also, what about the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We didn't find it on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be that the killer still has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:12.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where is the culprit's weapon?
